now lets try the weighted regression and start with calculating the weights

residl<-resid(fit)%>%abs()
fited<-fitted(fit)
residfit<-lm(residl~fited)
fittresid<-fitted(residfit)
wts<-1/fittresid^2

wtsfit<-houses%>%with(lm(price~.,data=houses,weights = wts))
summary(wtsfit)
